metadata.name: PSC-1
metadata.description:
Blue Suitcase 

I planned a trip the other day
The preparation was thorough and true
I unpacked for this trip. 
Everything that was too heavy to move
Photos of family gatherings,
The love that was shared, 
Happy Birthdays left aside,
Hugs from all who had cared, 
These smiles are not needed,  
The baby book can stay too, 
My trip does not need 
happy baggage from you  
I am packing one thing
in this suitcase of blue 
The one thing I packed
Was my life 
Without you

     Written and Recorded without a studio or paying other people to make me sound good.

      I wrote this while in a Twitter space supporting NFT artists. This was inspired by an artist who had the idea to end their life just like I have thought of before. Be kind to one another. Show love and support.
